50|$|A durable {{solution}} is identified {{on the basis}} of a best interests’ determination and it is therefore different for each individual unaccompanied or <b>separated</b> <b>child,</b> including refugees and asylum seekers, and children who are victims of trafficking. Its longer-term objectives ensure the child’s safety, well-being and development. It leads to family reunification or alternative care arrangements according to the best interests of the child.|$|E
